txt.en: The note appears to be written in a complex cipher. This is something that you have never seen before in your travels. Perhaps the emissary will know more of what this means. You should deliver the note to them.
You discovered a note written in a strange cipher on the body of Sûbodal. Deliver it to  Girgish, Khôltekh's emissary.

She takes the note.

'What is this?'

Glancing over the parchment, she clicks her tongue.

'Curious. This is not a cipher with which I am familiar. It is good that you brought this to me. I will investigate this matter. Thank you for your effort.'
Deliver the cryptic note to Girgish at the crest of Jax Phanâl

You discovered a note on the body of the Haradrim sorcerer. You cannot make any sense of the symbols used on the note but can reason that it is writing of some type. This is likely something that Girgish should see. Return it to her at Jax Phanâl.
Deliver the cryptic note to Girgish at the crest of Jax Phanâl
